sequenceDiagram
    actor Student
    participant StudentDashboard as Student Dashboard
    participant AdaptiveController as Adaptive Practice Controller
    participant KnowledgeModel as Knowledge Model (FSRS)
    participant Database

    Note over Student,StudentDashboard: UC-03: Solve Practice Sheet (Adaptive)

    Student->>StudentDashboard: Initiates practice session
    StudentDashboard->>AdaptiveController: startPracticeSession(studentId)
    AdaptiveController->>KnowledgeModel: identifyDueTopics(studentId)
    KnowledgeModel-->>AdaptiveController: List of due topics and scaffolding tier

    alt No topics due
        AdaptiveController-->>StudentDashboard: Status: "All caught up"
        StudentDashboard-->>Student: Notify: "Review mastered topics?"
    else Topics available
        AdaptiveController->>Database: getQuestion(topicId, tier)
        Database-->>AdaptiveController: Question data
        AdaptiveController-->>StudentDashboard: Display question

        opt Student requests explanation video
            Student->>StudentDashboard: Clicks "Watch Explanation"
            StudentDashboard->>AdaptiveController: requestExplanation(questionId)
            AdaptiveController->>Database: getVideoUrl(questionId)
            Database-->>AdaptiveController: Video URL
            AdaptiveController-->>StudentDashboard: Play video
            StudentDashboard-->>Student: Plays video, then returns to question
        end

        Student->>StudentDashboard: Submits answer
        StudentDashboard->>AdaptiveController: submitResponse(answer)
        AdaptiveController->>AdaptiveController: Grade answer (immediate)
        AdaptiveController-->>StudentDashboard: Feedback & model solution

        Note right of AdaptiveController: Update model and progress
        AdaptiveController->>KnowledgeModel: calculateNewParameters(currentStability, difficulty, success)
        KnowledgeModel-->>AdaptiveController: New stability, difficulty, next review

        par Database updates
            AdaptiveController->>Database: updateTopicMastery(stability, difficulty, nextReview)
            AdaptiveController->>Database: logAttempt(studentId, questionId, result)
            AdaptiveController->>Database: updateStudentStats(addXP, incrementStreak)
        end

        AdaptiveController-->>StudentDashboard: Return updated progress (XP, streak)
        StudentDashboard-->>Student: Update dashboard & leaderboard
    end